# 🔱 AEGIS SYSTEM CONFIGURATION
# Instructions: Copy this file, rename the copy to ".env", and fill in your details.
# NEVER share your real .env file or upload it to GitHub!

# 1. Your Discord Bot Token (From Developer Portal > Bot > Reset Token)
TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

# 2. Your Personal Discord User ID (Right-click your name in Discord > Copy User ID)
# This is required for the Master Console (? commands) to recognize you.
OWNER_ID=your_personal_id_here

# 3. Your Bot's Application ID (From Developer Portal > General Information)
# Required for the deploy script to register your 30+ slash commands.
CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
